Summary: This sub-phase investigates whether Public should experiment with Engram-style tool-profile packaging similar to `ProfileAgent` and `ProfileAdmin`, but only as a delivery-layer teaching aid. It studies token savings, operator clarity, and failure modes without changing tool registration or ownership. It does not reduce the current tool surface or ship a new authority lane.
